userdoc.notice: Simple contract to detect if a given address represents an Argent wallet. The `isArgentWallet` method returns true if the codehash matches one of the deployed Proxy and if the target implementation matches one of the deployed BaseWallet. Only the owner of the contract can add code hash and implementations.
